Barbie against stereotypes.
Gender dolls
Barbie's manufacturer has placed a series of sexually neutral dolls on the market.
That's how he wants to fight stereotypes.
Barbie manufacturer launched a series of sexually neutral dolls
Next to Barbie of different skin color, figure or hairstyle, Mattel introduced a gender-neutral doll to the sale.
